/* Table: "MD_Company" */
/*==============================================================*/
create table "MD_Company"
(
"CompanyID" NUMBER(32) not null,
"CompanyCode" VARCHAR2(20),
"CompanyName" NVARCHAR2(200),
"StartTime" TIMESTAMP,
"EndTime" TIMESTAMP,
"Enable" INTEGER default 1 not null,
"CreateBy" NUMBER(32) not null,
"CreateTime" TIMESTAMP default SYSDATE not null,
"ModifyBy" NUMBER(32),
"ModifyTime" TIMESTAMP,
constraint PK_MD_COMPANY primary key ("CompanyID")
);
